data.description: Experience the tranquil living at Summerwood Condominiums! Enjoy amenities like a pool and tennis court, all set in a beautiful wooded landscape. This spacious end-unit townhouse features 2 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a fireplace. Additional features include gas heating, wood-style laminate floors on the first level, and large closets in the well-sized bedrooms. The unit also boasts replacement white vinyl windows, a patio accessible via a sliding door, and an open eat-in kitchen. The full basement includes a finished, heated family room. Located just minutes from Mashpee Commons, you'll have quick access to all your shopping and entertainment needs.
